{"tid":1161052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肯亞總統拜訪中國後驚傳失蹤 當地民眾發起尋人活動","createTime":"2019-05-19T01:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T04:06:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"88e8c571d96e20a5b55e24156481ffbeb32c2a31","tid":1161052,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpgOm6Cn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpgOm6Cn.jpg&h=949a8d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肯亞總統甘耶達（Uhuru Kenyatta）4月造訪中國與習近平會晤，但肯亞民眾懷疑總統自那以後就失蹤了，因此在網路上發起尋人啟事，希望各界能幫忙找人。（圖擷自@JustinTribly推特）<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-19 09:34<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕去一趟中國就被消失了？肯亞總統甘耶達（Uhuru Kenyatta）4月造訪中國與習近平會晤，但肯亞民眾如今卻憂心忡忡，因為總統自那以後似乎都沒有出席任何公開行程，當地網友們在推特上發起「#FindPresidentUhuru」尋人活動，提供甘耶達的基本訊息，希望各界能幫忙找人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php404uhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php404uhw.jpg&h=632aa1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肯亞總統甘耶達4月在北京與習近平握手。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n據《CNN》報導，甘耶達上個月前往北京參加第二屆一帶一路論壇，拜會了中國國家主席習近平，並與中國達成了雙邊協議。然而，尋人活動直指甘耶達從中國行以來就一直沒有公開露面。<br />\n<br />\n肯亞總統辦公室發言人迪娜（Kanze Dena）對甘耶達消失的傳聞做出否認，強調總統沒出現在公共場合並不代表他失蹤了，因為他每天都有進辦公室處理政務。<br />\n<br />\n迪娜說，總統其實有出席5月初國際衛生組織全球基金會的會議，但她承認自己並沒有完全向外界說明總統的行程，因此她承諾未來會和大眾與記者分享相關資訊。<br />\n<br />\n不過，肯亞民眾對總統辦公室的說法仍然存疑，並要求甘耶達重新使用推特和臉書，因為總統這兩個社交平台自3月被停用後，一直都沒有重啟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2794910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2794910&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=c2e1ee47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2794910&h=93931f05\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2794910</a>"},{"pid":"7d9d798c36bddb99a19d58695dc6f0d19fdcb5e6","tid":1161052,"uid":49197,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:40:42.000Z","msg":"甘耶達:習先生,你俾我D極品女仔我屌返一頭半個月,我就同你簽協議<br />\n習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />K"},{"pid":"1648824d976f4f0b7351319b1126f35864f37c59","tid":1161052,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甘耶達:習先生,你俾我D極品女仔我屌返一頭半個月,我就同你簽協議<br />\n習近平: OK</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5c4cf93bdeb339b9790a3594d157c602391af2a9","tid":1161052,"uid":25468,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:09:55.000Z","msg":"肯亞好似啱啱話支那幫佢哋起果個機場合約有問題，中途停止左，肯亞唔肯賠錢，打緊官司"},{"pid":"0dca17c28181042ff6937d7220eb9891ee3a336c","tid":1161052,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"中國有句古話：兩國交戰，不斬來使"},{"pid":"bc81ed20b7f3ca5541538a588ec0291856f9735e","tid":1161052,"uid":73856,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"0dca17c28181042ff6937d7220eb9891ee3a336c","tid":1161052,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"中國有句古話：兩國交戰，不斬來使"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"直接斬大佬"},{"pid":"d4d632d49512c1d724e748b30a996e8afe1d9a04","tid":1161052,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"已經復制左個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好快調較完還返俾你啦，仲嘈！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ccb529a72da7df676e74588929a953783927e9","tid":1161052,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"天上人間"},{"pid":"c51d45a10016e6b58273f11ddcfd31d0b4e2ee1e","tid":1161052,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dca17c28181042ff6937d7220eb9891ee3a336c","tid":1161052,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"